          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2020-03-05T22:59:14Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Property Rights for Patriots Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a homeowners association from seeking to enforce a policy (1) that restricts the right of a member to lease the real property of such member, and (2) against a servicemember whose residence is that property during a period of military service of at least 90 days. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-09-16T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
